		</div>		<div class="post-byline">By Septravarius, on May 10th, 2011%</div>		<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><div class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style " addthis:url='http://www.altnews.info/826/fukushima-reactor-4-leaning-and-in-danger-of-exposing-spent-fuel-rods/' addthis:title='Fukushima Reactor 4 &#8220;leaning&#8221; and in danger of exposing spent fuel rods '  ><a class="addthis_button_facebook_like" fb:like:layout="button_count"></a><a class="addthis_button_tweet"></a><a class="addthis_counter addthis_pill_style"></a></div><p>httpv://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dxbm7iJTT8U&#038;feature=player_embedded</p>
